Silence:
She walked away from the office in an absolute fury. She talked under
her breath, "How can any Maximal in thier right mental capacities make
an allience with someone so untrustowrthy as a Depticon."  She made
her way to the mess hall.  She stopped at the doorway just outside
since raised voices were over heard. No, now is not a good time to
interupt, she thought.  She turned and went to the observation point.
 She leaned on the rail and looked around. "Why? I don't undestand."
She lowered her head and tried to think past the darkness that filled
her past. All she knew right then was she held the biggest grudge
against Decepticons and Predacons.  So far, they had not harmed her
and an allience with them to soolve this one opponate that could wipe
them all out was a logical answer. But still, she could not understand
her own rage. Only that she hated them. She sighed deeply and tried to
find answersm somewhere in the lost data in the back of her memory banks.
